*-- Notes:
*   Fixed values provide automatic F4 help and validation
*   Values map to UI5 MessageType:
*     HIGH = Error (Red)
*     MEDIUM = Warning (Orange)
*     LOW = Information (Blue)
*   Tile counter uses HIGH count for color-coding:
*     ≥3 HIGH = Red tile
*     1-2 HIGH = Orange tile
*     0 HIGH = Green tile
